                    <span>RP's new edition of Bordeaux gave me one impression. You have no choice but to buy it if you are really interested in Bordeaux wine. I have his Wine Buyer's Guide (6th Ed) and yet find this one irresistable when I first located it in a book shop.</span>
                  
              
